    "Thomas G. Long": "Laborers for the Plentiful Harvest\n[v_Mat_9_35] Matthew 9:35 10:42\n112\nShepherds and Farm Workers (9:35 38)\n112\nThe Twelve Disciples (10:1 4)\n113\nA Manual for Missionaries (10:5 15)\n115\nDisciples Can Expect Persecution (10:16 39)\n119\nThe Rewards (10:40 42)\n122\n< previous page\npage_vi\nnext page >\nfile:///D|/Gigapedia/Bible%20Studies/0664252575__gigle.ws/0664252575/files/page_vi.html\uff08\u7b2c 2\uff0f2 \u9875\uff092010-11-7 6:27:16\npage_vii\n< previous page\npage_vii\nnext page >\nPage vii"
